    <body>
      <section eId="sec_160_GG">
        <num>160-GG</num>
        <heading>Plan of operation</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish procedures for collecting and managing the assets of the\nfund;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish regular places and times for meetings of the fund's\nboard of directors;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish the procedure by which the fund shall determine whether\nto provide the benefits due pursuant to this article by self-insuring or\nby purchasing insurance;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish accounting and record-keeping procedures for all\nfinancial transactions of the fund, its agents and the board of\ndirectors;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish a procedure for determining and collecting the\nappropriate amount of surcharges and assessments under this article;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_f">
          <num>(f)</num>
          <content>
            <p>set forth the procedures by which the fund may exercise the audit\nrights granted to it under this article;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_g">
          <num>(g)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish procedures to ensure prompt and accurate notification to\nthe fund by its members of all accidents and injuries to black car\noperators, and provide for full reimbursement of the fund by any central\ndispatch facility whose failure to provide such notification results in\nthe imposition of a penalty on the fund by the board; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GG__subsec_h">
          <num>(h)</num>
          <content>
            <p>contain such additional provisions as the board of the fund may\ndeem necessary or proper for the execution of the powers and duties of\nthe fund.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
